-- QBE Insurance to buy Winterthur
-- 
-- Thu Jan 4, 2007 5:33pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/01/04/businesspro-winterthur-qbe-dc-idUSSYU00145320070104

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - QBE Insurance Group Ltd. ( QBE.AX ), 
Australia's top insurer by premium income, on Friday announced 
the acquisition of U.S. property and casualty insurer 
Winterthur US Holdings for US$1.16 billion, subject to 
regulatory approval. 

  Winterthur, based in Wisconsin, writes property and 
casualty insurance risks through 1,700 independent agents in 33 
states of the U.S. Its gross premium income for 2007 is 
expected to be around US$1.45 billion.